OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start for some in the
OL,6,Fnorth, however cloud further south and
OL,7,Fwest will spread northwards throughout
OL,8,Fthe day. Patchy rain initially over
OL,9,Fsouthern hills, but heavy downpours
OL,10,Ffor parts of the northwest in the
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,14,Fwith hill fog likely. Cloud thick
OL,15,Fenough to bring outbreaks of light
OL,16,Frain and drizzle on higher ground.
OL,17,FMild and feeling muggy for some in the
OL,18,Fsouth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
