OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAnother cloudy start to the
OL,6,Fday with some brightness developing in
OL,7,Fthe east later where it will feel
OL,8,Fwarm. Some light rain along western
OL,9,Fcoasts at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,12,Fmore settled into the weekend as high
OL,13,Fpressure starts to build from the
OL,14,Fsouth. Sunny spells and feeling very
OL,15,Fwarm with temperatures well above the
OL,16,FJune average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
